text: Deormod gebohte æt Ælfred cyninge mid fiftigum mancessan arodenes goldes fif hida land on ece yrfe ælces þinges freoh butan fyrde & fæstingeweorces on þisum land fæst.
Ærest on þa lace þæ lið be westan dyrnangelade &lang lace up on ane furh<../images/tbar.gif>on widan geat &lang dic.
<../images/tbar.gif>on þone mor ðe led betwux suðtune & wittanhamme & swa forð be more<../images/tbar.gif>on þa ealdan dic þæ lið betwux wigbaldincgtune & Appelforda.
And of þære ealdan dic to dices wyllan of dices wyllan to sand gewyrpe.
